 * Generate a random name and output it to the chat.
 * generateText() takes the name of the Roll Table to use
 * in the "NPC Generator" folder.
 *
 * First parameter is the base name of the table.
 * Second (optional) parameter is the variant.
 * Third (optional) parameter is name of folder.
 *
 * Variant is appended to the base table name, and if not, falls
 * back to looking for the base table name.
 */

